Field record

Source: R/data-twogases_record.R
twogases_record.Rd

Field record

Usage

twogases_record

Format

A tibble with 12 rows and 1 variable

start

Start datetime of each flux measurement

Examples

twogases_record
#> # A tibble: 12 × 1
#>    start              
#>    <dttm>             
#>  1 2024-06-18 10:04:27
#>  2 2024-06-18 11:12:42
#>  3 2024-06-18 11:16:31
#>  4 2024-06-18 11:38:46
#>  5 2024-06-18 11:42:40
#>  6 2024-06-18 12:59:33
#>  7 2024-06-18 13:37:35
#>  8 2024-06-18 14:35:32
#>  9 2024-06-18 14:39:32
#> 10 2024-06-18 15:02:59
#> 11 2024-06-18 15:07:28
#> 12 2024-06-18 16:18:36
